Text: The tracker isn't showing the seeders and leachers correctly for some reason.  There are a dozen or so leachers and three seeders right now, though the tracker shows 0/0.

the update betwenn tpb site / tracker database is slow, so even if ut, vuze etc says for exampel: 20 seeders and 100 leechers, the tpb site mayby show: 10 seeders and 70 leechers, because the update between the tracker system / site is slow. its a known problem.
